{"tid":1486202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今日4點記招問題］818集會警察倒果為因誣陷示威者惡意佔路 170萬人唔佔路點疏散？","createTime":"2019-08-18T20:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:52:20.000Z","uid":221265,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7298c3da3350ff19f9a810f459b1cca7bd9c6f","tid":1486202,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:06:41.000Z","msg":"170萬人散去唔佔路嘅話<br />\n係咪想我哋喺行人路人踩人/逼到窒息？<br />\n而且係佢哋倒果為因<br />\n唔批遊行<br />\n170萬人如何可以流水式出入維園<br />\n又唔佔維園一帶道路離開到？<br />\n（我姑且當你話深夜夏愨道佔路係冇必要講得通）<br />\n警察啲仆街冇邏輯言論<br />\n完全只係講俾撐警藍絲聽"},{"pid":"aeba39999a872475a31a9223fcc27222178811d7","tid":1486202,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3L2HuRS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3L2HuRS.jpg&h=a6ca7edf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWmQDLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWmQDLc.png&h=9adc7ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯署網址: <br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=44acd833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"41adaa69129d9b64705f06bfaa9bc0b758a6ebd3","tid":1486202,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:16:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9f9681432a289aa98ddc715a94769f12d9c65cef","tid":1486202,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:23:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3L2HuRS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3L2HuRS.jpg&h=a6ca7edf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWmQDLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWmQDLc.png&h=9adc7ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯署網址: <br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=44acd833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"a52dc9165b4ca2b43e23bc85a0fd6adc6923657a","tid":1486202,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:23:20.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=44acd833\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=44acd833\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"7fa250f55c8579314499327cb2eced336cad307d","tid":1486202,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:23:48.000Z","msg":"借推<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇留意，今日8點幾9點嘅時候，夏愨道D車係一堆咁連續駛入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d4d32c8a20bd2232b1ce3247fc9809ebd4c9780c","tid":1486202,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74EF18n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74EF18n.png&h=607cff02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28353207f14afed16337910684e02e908ccbae30","tid":1486202,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e9426e9ff40cda76da22820c2d224b51ff258403","tid":1486202,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}